<div class="section-title">Maintenance Mode</div>

<!-- Hero Toggle Card -->
<div class="mt-hero-card">
  <div class="mt-hero-left">
    <div class="mt-hero-icon off" id="sys-mt-icon">
      <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-hero-info">
      <div class="mt-hero-title">Maintenance Mode</div>
      <div class="mt-hero-sub" id="sys-mt-sub">Website berjalan normal. Aktifkan untuk menampilkan halaman perawatan.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <label class="mt-toggle-btn">
    <input type="checkbox" id="sys-mt-toggle" onchange="mobToggleMt(this.checked)">
    <span class="mt-toggle-slider"></span>
  </label>
</div>

<!-- Message Editor -->
<div class="app-card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <span class="card-header-title">Pesan Maintenance</span>
    <span class="card-header-sub">Ditampilkan ke pengguna saat maintenance aktif</span>
  </div>
  <div style="padding:12px 16px 16px;">
    <textarea id="sys-mt-message" class="mt-textarea" rows="4" placeholder="Website sedang dalam perbaikan. Silakan kembali lagi nanti." oninput="updatePreview()">Website sedang dalam perbaikan. Silakan kembali lagi nanti.</textarea>
    <div class="mt-msg-actions">
      <span class="mt-msg-hint">Pesan ini muncul di halaman maintenance yang dilihat pengunjung.</span>
      <button class="btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="mobSaveMtMsg()">
        <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 21H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11l5 5v11a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/><polyline points="17,21 17,13 7,13 7,21"/><polyline points="7,3 7,8 15,8"/></svg>
        Simpan Pesan
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="sys-mt-feedback" class="mt-feedback" style="display:none;"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Preview Card -->
<div class="app-card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <span class="card-header-title">Preview Halaman Maintenance</span>
    <span class="card-header-sub">Tampilan yang dilihat pengguna</span>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-preview-frame">
    <div class="mt-preview-content">
      <div class="mt-preview-icon">🔧</div>
      <div class="mt-preview-title">Website Sedang Dalam Perbaikan</div>
      <div class="mt-preview-msg" id="sys-mt-preview-msg">Website sedang dalam perbaikan. Silakan kembali lagi nanti.</div>
      <div class="mt-preview-sub">— Tim gpieluzaikids</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Info Card -->
<div class="app-card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <span class="card-header-title">Informasi</span>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-info-body">
    <div class="mt-info-item">
      <div class="mt-info-icon blue">
        <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-info-text">
        <div class="mt-info-title">Halaman yang diblokir</div>
        <div class="mt-info-desc">Saat maintenance aktif, semua request ke halaman publik (/, /events, /documentation) akan dialihkan ke halaman maintenance. Halaman admin tetap dapat diakses.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-info-item">
      <div class="mt-info-icon green">
        <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-info-text">
        <div class="mt-info-title">Halaman yang tetap aktif</div>
        <div class="mt-info-desc">Jalur /admin/*, /dev/*, dan /api/* tetap berfungsi normal. Dev dan admin masih bisa login dan bekerja selama maintenance.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-info-item">
      <div class="mt-info-icon orange">
        <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-info-text">
        <div class="mt-info-title">Perhatian</div>
        <div class="mt-info-desc">Matikan maintenance mode setelah selesai. Pengguna tidak bisa mengakses website selama mode ini aktif.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
